{"word":"ἀπολογέομαι","slug":"ἀπολογέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀπολογέομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λόγος\">λόγος</a></el>] ‘speak in one’s own defense’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> with contextual component of spurious charges in juristic proceedings, <b><i>defend oneself</i> <a href='B:490 21:14'>Lk 21:14</a>; <a href='B:510 19:33'>Ac 19:33</a>; <a href='B:510 26:1'>26:1</a>; <a href='B:540 12:19'>2 Cor 12:19</a>;</b> followed by <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὅτι\">ὅτι</a></el><b> <a href='B:510 25:8'>Ac 25:8</a>;</b> with <el>τί</el> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> stated in self-defense <b><a href='B:490 12:11'>Lk 12:11</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:510 24:10'>Ac 24:10</a>; <a href='B:510 26:24'>26:24</a>;</b> with <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:περί\">περί</a></el> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to charges <b><a href='B:510 26:2'>26:2</a>.</b> Cp. <b><a href='B:520 2:15'>Ro 2:15</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Ἀπολλῶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπολογία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}